appDesc.message: Musa ukuchitha isikhathi sakho ngokuhambisana. I-FastForward ivimbela izifinyezo ezihluphayo zesixhumanisi.

beforeNavigateOptions.message: Ufuna ukuphinde uqondiswe kabusha noma ngemizuzwana eyi-x?

beforeNavigateUnsafe.message: Kodwa-ke, uma uzulazula manje, bazobona i-FastForward.

blockedSubtitle.message: Ngabe awufuni i-FastForward ukuvikela abenzi ababi ekutholeni i-IP yakho?

blockedTitle.message: I-FastForward ivimbele i-IP yakho ukuthi ingangeni.

bypassCounter.message: I-FastForward isivele idlule kuwe amasayithi we-%.

crowdBypassedInfo.message: Abanye abasebenzisi be-FastForward sebevele bakulindile futhi babika ukuthi lokhu kuholela ku-%

crowdBypassedOptions.message: Ngabe ufuna ukuthi lokhu kuvulwe kuthebhu entsha ngokushesha noma ngemizuzwana eyi-x?

crowdBypassedTimer.message: Lokhu kuzovulwa kuthebhu entsha ngemizuzwana engu-%.

crowdBypassedTimerSingular.message: Lokhu kuzovulwa kuthebhu entsha kusekhondi eli-1.

crowdDisabled.message: Le webhusayithi idluliswa ukudlula kwesixuku, esikhubaze kukho ongakhetha kukho.

crowdWait.message: Ngeshwa, ungowokuqala ukuhlangana nalesi sixhumanisi, kepha ngemuva kokuthi usulindile, abanye abasebenzisi be-FastForward ngeke kusadingeka.

firstrunNoScript.message: Noma kunjalo, ubonakala ngathi usebenzisa i-NoScript noma efanayo, i-FastForward engahambelani nayo.

infoFileHoster.message: Ngeshwa, iseva yokulanda izoqinisekisa ukuthi ulindile ngaphambi kokukuvumela ukuthi ulande ifayela.

infoOutdated.message: Le webhusayithi iphambukiswa yinguqulo entsha ye-Universal Diversion.

optionsCrowdAutoClose.message: Vala ithebhu equkethe indawo okutholwe kuyo isixuku ngemuva kwe-% yesibili yokuyi vakashela.

optionsCrowdAutoOpen.message: Vula izindawo okutholwe izixuku kuthebhu entsha ngemuva kwama-% wesibili.

optionsCrowdBypass.message: Nikeza futhi uthathe izindawo ezinqamulelayo ezingashintshiwe.

optionsInstantNavigationTrackers.message: Ngihambise masinya lapho ngiya khona kubasebenzisi be-trackers.

optionsUserscriptsDescription.message: Lesi isici esithuthukisiwe sonjiniyela bokuzenzela imibhalo yabo ezizeni ezidlula. Lapho sebesetshenzisiwe, bangafakwa ku-GitHub ukuthi ingezwe ku-FastForward, ngakho-ke batholakala kuwo wonke umuntu.
